A utility library for Atmel AVR microcontrollers.

On Windows you'll need WinAVR (from http://winavr.sourceforge.net)

On Linux you'll need gcc-avr and avr-libc (sudo apt-get install...)

chris@wotan$ curl -sL http://www.swaton.ukfsn.org/bin/makestuff-lindar-20110912.tar.gz | tar zxf -
chris@wotan$ cd makestuff/libs
chris@wotan$ ../common/msget.sh avrlib
chris@wotan$ cd avrlib
chris@wotan$ make

or, if you want an atmega162 build:

chris@wotan$  make MCU=atmega162
